nded-full bg-[#B45309] animate-pulse\"></span> Warning\n                            </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-sm mb-md\">\n<div class=\"bg-[#FEF3C7]/30 p-sm rounded-lg border border-[#F59E0B]/30\">\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-[#B45309] block mb-1\">Coolant Pressure</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm font-mono-data text-[#B45309]\">2.1 bar <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] align-middle\">arrow_downward</span></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-sm rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/50\">\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant block mb-1\">Vibration</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm font-mono-data text-on-surface\">0.4 mm/s</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-error flex items-center gap-xs\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]\">info</span>\n                            Coolant pressure is below the standard threshold. Inspect promptly.\n                        </div>\n</div>\n<!-- Machine Card 3: Idle -->\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-xl p-md opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-md\">\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm text-on-surface\">Robotic-Arm-Assembly-2</h3>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-body-sm text-on-surface-variant\">Line B · Assembly Cell</p>\n</div>\n<span class=\"px-2 py-1 rounded bg-surface-container text-on-surface-variant text-label-md font-label-md flex items-center gap-xs\">\n<span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-outline\"></span> Idle\n                            </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-sm mb-md\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-sm rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/50\">\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant block mb-1\">Average Joint Temp</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm font-mono-data text-on-surface-variant\">31.0 °C</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-sm rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/50\">\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant block mb-1\">Power Draw</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm font-mono-data text-on-surface-variant\">0.5 kW</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant italic\">Awaiting material loading.</p>\n</div>\n<!-- Machine Card 4: Running -->\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-xl p-md hover:shadow-[0px_4px_6px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] transition-shadow\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-md\">\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm text-on-surface\">Stamp-Press-09</h3>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-body-sm text-on-surface-variant\">Zone D · Forming Press</p>\n</div>\n<span class=\"px-2 py-1 rounded bg-[#E6F4EA] text-[#137333] text-label-md font-label-md flex items-center gap-xs\">\n<span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#137333]\"></span> Running\n                            </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-sm mb-md\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-sm rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/50\">\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant block mb-1\">Cycle Count</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm font-mono-data text-on-surface\">12,450</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-sm rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/50\">\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant block mb-1\">Press Force</span>\n<span class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm font-mono-data text-on-surface\">240 kN</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Right Panel: Equipment Maintenance & Logs -->\n<div class=\"xl:col-span-4 space-y-gutter\">\n<!-- Equipment Maintenan