ication</span>\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant\">Tomorrow</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-body-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">CNC-Milling-01 • Zone A</p>\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-sm\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-on-surface-variant\">pending</span>\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant\">Unassigned</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- List Item 3 -->\n<div class=\"p-md hover:bg-[#F8FAFC] transition-colors cursor-pointer rounded-b-xl\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-1\">\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface font-bold\">Q3 Calibration Check</span>\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant\">In 3 Days</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-body-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">All Stamp Presses · Zone D</p>\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-sm\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-on-surface-variant\">pending</span>\n<span class=\"text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant\">Unassigned</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Failure Records Snapshot -->\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-xl p-md\">\n<h2 class=\"text-headline-sm font-headline-sm text-on-surface border-b border-outline-variant pb-xs mb-sm flex items-center gap-xs\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-error\">history</span>\n                        Recent Failure Logs\n                    </h2>\n<ul class=\"space-y-sm\">\n<li class=\"flex gap-sm items-start text-body-sm font-body-sm text-on-surface\">\n<span class=\"text-error font-mono-data mt-1\">ERR-92</span>\n<div>\n<span class=\"block font-semibold\">Conveyor-Belt-Main</span>\n<span class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-label-md font-label-md\">Motor stall detected. Reset applied. (2 hrs ago)</span>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-sm items-start text-body-sm font-body-s